  src.java.util.Tree

class Tree

See TreeList, but uses a string for the key instead of an integer index, also is backed by a map.

nextOrder

private int nextOrder(IndexedTreeMap map)
Returns the next available order from a map. It will count up from MID until it finds an empty spot. This is so the map maintains the order items were added.
